Classes
Class
Description
Postnet_Generator
The Postnet_Generator class can generate postnet barcodes, and binary representations of 5 digit US zipcodes
Postnet_Reader
The Postnet_Reader can transform a binary string back into a 5 digit us zipcode
UPCA_Decoder
The UPCA_Decoder class decodes 95 digit UPC-A barcodes into 11 digit product codes
UPCA_Encoder
The UPCA_Encoder class encodes 11 digit product codes into 95 digit UPCA barcodes
